<p>About Nova</p>
<p2>This website is intended to allow people to enjoy their favorite retro games whenever they want. However, we are not responsible for misuse of the site. If you get in trouble, that's kinda on you, buddy. Because people might disobey what we just said in the previous sentence, like PLAYHYDRA, Nova will switch websites any time the website gets blocked as to keep the emulators and ROMs archived.
On a legal note, however. If you'd like to see the Terms and Conditions (if you're so inclined) click <a href="https://nova-games.w3spaces.com/terms.html">here.</a></p2>
